\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid334622\charrsid14430778 Elsie}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778  May Knight. 123 Richmond Avenue.
