\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 How many years did you live in the house }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid334622\charrsid14430778 where you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
