 at Vickers - Erith. And I think we went from - Erith to Northumberland }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid334622\charrsid14430778 H}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 
eath. Northumberland Heath, that is it - a part of Kent. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid334622\charrsid14430778 Near Erith and Northumberland Heath and all round there. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 
And if I can remember rightly we were living at Northumberland Heath when my grandmother sent to my mother to say her brother had died and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid334622\charrsid14430778 they}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
