d started. I - as - well I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 How old were you when you moved to Plumstead?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 
Oh now - before that - we lived at - we lived over a dentists in - I think that was Erith if I can remember rightly. And then we went from there to Northumber
land Heath. And then we came to live with my grandmother, this is more that I can remember vividly, and we come to live with my grandmother in 19 - the war started in 1914 didn't it - well I think we'd just come up to grandma's before the war started. I'm
 nine - nine or ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Do you remember why the family made these moves, why your father went down to Southampton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Well he had - it was his job you see, yes, it was his work. Yes. Yes. He had to come back on different - 'cos he worked at }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid334622\charrsid14430778 Thorneycroft\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 
