urse I mean you're asking me details and I've got to give them to you, you see. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Well then after we were living with my grandmother in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid334622\charrsid14430778 Plumstead}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 , and after I lost my mother my father had a nervous breakdown. We had to sell up the home. The two boys went dow
n to the convent at Southend and I had to go out into domestic service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 So this would be the beginning of 1918?
