Oh yes. My youngest brother was - he was - was eighteen months when - he was born in 1918. '16 rather, and my other brother was born in 1908 - '08 - 'cos I'm four years older than him. Is that right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
