\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 They were both about the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Yes, my mother - I think my mother was a little bit older than my father as far as I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Where did he come from?
