\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Their friends would come to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 
People often tell us that people in those days made their own amusements, what do you think your parents did when they got together with their friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Oh - sit and talk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Would they have a musical evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Or play cards or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 No. No. Just - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15950258\charrsid14430778 social}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778  - social calling, that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Many people divide society into different social classes or groups, in that time before 1918 did }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
