\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Well, there were more or less }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15950258\charrsid14430778 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
