\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Well they had more money. Position. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Did you come in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11025434\charrsid14430778 contact}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
