Well - I should imagine the people that - well people of our own standard you know, and people that are a bit more - business people and - people like that. And some - well, so called gentry. Well the ge
ntry, they used to go to their own - church don't they and - but - well the gentry, they - they go wherever they live, if they attended church they'd go to that church. Well now when I was at the Rectory, well of course my mistress and master whatever you
 call him, they used to go to the church away from where we lived. They were at Highwood - at South - not - Woodford, Woodford Green but then they sometimes Mr - the Reverend Harris used to preach at the old Rectory church. See what I mean?
