\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Not the chapel, no. Well - since I've been going down to - you know Mr Brya
nt, 'cos he'd - he's a chapel. I've gone from Catholic to chapel. But that's nothing to go by.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 You were church of England as a child though?
