\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Were some families thought of as rough and others respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8013821 EK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Yes, in some cases.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5922958 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11299755\charrsid14430778 Could you give us any description of this?
